{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"conversion-control-center\">\n<h1>Conversion control center<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#conversion-control-center\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>The Conversion Control Center is where you manage all your work.</p>\n<img alt=\"../../_images/cc_view.png\" src=\"../../_images/cc_view.png\" />\n<p>The links behind the <strong>Contents folder</strong> give you access to your configured contents folder.\nThe eye icon will give you view access to the content folder while the pencil icon will\nopen the first content object in edit mode.</p>\n<img alt=\"../../_images/cc_content_folder.png\" src=\"../../_images/cc_content_folder.png\" />\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"inspectors\">\n<h2>Inspectors<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#inspectors\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>The Conversion Control Center comes with several inspectors that allow you to\ncheck several aspects of your authoring project for consistency.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"image-inspector\">\n<h3>Image inspector<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#image-inspector\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>The image inspectors displays all referenced images (in thumbnail size)\ntogether with all conversion related parameters. The most common problem are\nimages without a description. The description is used for the caption of an\nimage and therefore must be filled out. An image with a  missing description\nwill be marked with an exclamation mark.</p>\n<img alt=\"../../_images/cc_inspector_image.png\" src=\"../../_images/cc_inspector_image.png\" />\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"anchor-inspector\">\n<h3>Anchor inspector<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#anchor-inspector\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>The anchor inspector shows all internal cross-references. Stale references will\nbe marked with an exclamation mark or a green check sign as shown in the\npicture.</p>\n<img alt=\"../../_images/cc_inspector_anchors.png\" src=\"../../_images/cc_inspector_anchors.png\" />\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"document-structure-inspector\">\n<h3>Document structure inspector<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#document-structure-inspector\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>The document structure inspector checks your document for logical errors. E.g.\na <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">H1</span></tt> heading can not be followed by a <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">H3</span></tt> heading.</p>\n<img alt=\"../../_images/cc_inspector_document_structure.png\" src=\"../../_images/cc_inspector_document_structure.png\" />\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"links-inspector\">\n<h3>Links inspector<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#links-inspector\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>For inspection completeness the Links inspector will list all links to external\npages including their link text.</p>\n<img alt=\"../../_images/cc_inspector_links.png\" src=\"../../_images/cc_inspector_links.png\" />\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"conversion-workflow\">\n<h2>Conversion workflow<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#conversion-workflow\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Every conversion output (PDF, EPUB etc.) will be stored in a dedicated\n<tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Drafts</span></tt> folder that you can see at the bottom of the conversions center\nview.</p>\n<img alt=\"../../_images/drafts_published.png\" src=\"../../_images/drafts_published.png\" />\n<p>All entries are sorted by creation date (newest first). By clicking on\nconversion result you can either download the generated file or view them\nwithin a browser (HTML + PDF conversion). Additional information about\nsize, creation date and creator is provided.</p>\n<p>If you are fine with conversion result then you can click on <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">publish/rename</span></tt>\nand the conversion result will be moved into the configured\n<tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Publications</span></tt> folder. The workflow state of all content will be automatically changed\nto state <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">published</span></tt>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "Conversion control center", "sourcename": "authoring/conversions_center.txt", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "authoring/conversions_center", "next": {"link": "../conversions/", "title": "Conversions"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["authoring/conversions", "Conversions", "N", "next"], ["authoring/manage_content", "Managing and organizing your content", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Conversion control center</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#inspectors\">Inspectors</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#image-inspector\">Image inspector</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#anchor-inspector\">Anchor inspector</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#document-structure-inspector\">Document structure inspector</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#links-inspector\">Links inspector</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#conversion-workflow\">Conversion workflow</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../manage_content/", "title": "Managing and organizing your content"}, "metatags": ""}